WEBVTT

00:00:36.478 --> 00:00:39.064
[Final Episode] Go tell Han Kyung Wook

00:00:39.064 --> 00:00:41.066
To prepare to pay for his sins.

00:00:41.066 --> 00:00:43.360
That's far too much arrogance.

00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:47.188
Isn't that something you say only after everything's over?

00:01:02.713 --> 00:01:06.883
Hey, you step aside.

00:01:06.883 --> 00:01:09.469
You're terrible at fighting anyway. I'll finish this.

00:01:09.469 --> 00:01:11.254
Bulgae!

00:01:12.597 --> 00:01:19.053
You haven't forgotten who taught you Taekkyeon, have you?

00:01:19.896 --> 00:01:23.150
Looks like you've gotten a lot more talkative while I wasn't around.

00:01:23.150 --> 00:01:25.268
Cut the nonsense,

00:01:28.029 --> 00:01:30.106
And come at me.

00:02:01.688 --> 00:02:03.306
<i>Focus.</i>

00:02:43.313 --> 00:02:45.398
Comrade Lieutenant,

00:02:45.398 --> 00:02:47.943
Your footwork doesn't seem as sharp as it used to be.

00:02:47.943 --> 00:02:50.186
You little punk!

00:02:57.285 --> 00:02:59.371
Comrade Lieutenant!

00:02:59.371 --> 00:03:01.322
Let's retreat for now.

00:03:07.504 --> 00:03:10.665
Wait, wait! Let him go.

00:03:14.177 --> 00:03:16.221
We finally caught him, and you're just letting him go?

00:03:16.221 --> 00:03:18.807
Yeah, he just left.

00:03:18.807 --> 00:03:20.100
Don't lose him. Follow him.

00:03:20.100 --> 00:03:21.968
Yes, understood.

00:03:34.322 --> 00:03:36.324
- Who is it? - It's Gong Bok.

00:03:36.324 --> 00:03:38.827
- He's back? - Yeah.

00:03:38.827 --> 00:03:42.497
He said he'd figure out what he needs to do himself.

00:03:42.497 --> 00:03:44.365
What about Beom Ryong?

00:03:47.460 --> 00:03:51.089
Let's help your nephew first.

00:03:51.089 --> 00:03:52.790
Nam Il!

00:03:54.718 --> 00:03:57.461
Nam Il, are you okay?

00:03:58.597 --> 00:04:00.298
Hurry.

00:04:03.643 --> 00:04:05.678
- Careful, careful, careful! - Careful.

00:04:09.816 --> 00:04:12.068
He rushed out saying there was a gas leak at home,

00:04:12.068 --> 00:04:13.904
But why are you carrying him back, Mr. Bong?

00:04:13.904 --> 00:04:15.405
Did he actually inhale gas or something?

00:04:15.405 --> 00:04:19.409
What gas? He probably got into trouble again and passed out somewhere.

00:04:19.409 --> 00:04:21.536
I'm sorry,

00:04:21.536 --> 00:04:25.165
But could you two look after Nam Il for a bit?

00:04:25.165 --> 00:04:27.042
I have something urgent to take care of, so I'll be leaving first.

00:04:27.042 --> 00:04:30.670
You're leaving just like this? Never thought you were that kind of person, Mr. Bong.

00:04:30.670 --> 00:04:34.424
Lately you disappear without saying anything. And now you're leaving your nephew behind.

00:04:34.424 --> 00:04:37.093
How can you be so irresponsible?

00:04:37.093 --> 00:04:38.136
I'm sorry.

00:04:38.136 --> 00:04:39.763
Wait, wait, Mr. Bong!

00:04:39.763 --> 00:04:44.017
Could you at least wait until Nam Il wakes up?

00:04:44.017 --> 00:04:46.728
He was really worried because he couldn't reach you.

00:04:46.728 --> 00:04:50.190
Ms. Lee, tell Nam Il

00:04:50.190 --> 00:04:53.735
- he doesn't need to worry about me anymore. - What?

00:04:53.735 --> 00:04:55.070
- Wait. - No, wait...

00:04:55.070 --> 00:04:57.113
Well, he...

00:04:57.113 --> 00:05:00.867
He's completely changed, hasn't he?

00:05:00.867 --> 00:05:03.027
Something must have happened, right?

00:05:10.251 --> 00:05:13.037
Why are you so worried about him? He's old enough.

00:05:13.713 --> 00:05:15.173
Old enough? Not really.

00:05:15.173 --> 00:05:17.968
He may look grown on the outside.

00:05:17.968 --> 00:05:21.054
But do you know how childish he still is?

00:05:21.054 --> 00:05:26.133
Nam Il won't even eat if he doesn't have sausage as a side dish.

00:05:27.268 --> 00:05:29.562
And he's scared of everything.

00:05:29.562 --> 00:05:33.733
He sleeps with the light on because he's scared of ghosts.

00:05:33.733 --> 00:05:36.727
And he's so unbelievably clumsy.

00:05:37.445 --> 00:05:41.074
He went to a high school where almost everyone graduates,

00:05:41.074 --> 00:05:45.036
But he got held back twice because he miscalculated his attendance days.

00:05:45.036 --> 00:05:48.873
This year, I really need to make sure he graduates,

00:05:48.873 --> 00:05:51.575
So he won't be called that legendary repeat student.

00:05:52.210 --> 00:05:54.879
You said you were going to leave without ever looking back.

00:05:54.879 --> 00:06:00.176
- You were acting like you were so cool. - I wasn't pretending. I really am cool.

00:06:00.176 --> 00:06:02.721
He's just been acting cold because he's going through puberty.

00:06:02.721 --> 00:06:05.140
When he was little, he used to cling to me,

00:06:05.140 --> 00:06:07.308
Always calling me Uncle.

00:06:07.308 --> 00:06:08.893
How could I not worry about him?

00:06:08.893 --> 00:06:14.504
So even the mighty Bulgae is getting emotional, huh?

00:06:14.504 --> 00:06:16.713
Haha, jeez.

00:06:18.778 --> 00:06:21.114
Is this car crawling or what? Step on it.

00:06:21.114 --> 00:06:22.323
I'm stepping on it!

00:06:22.323 --> 00:06:24.743
Step harder!

00:06:24.743 --> 00:06:28.621
We need to go faster if we're going to take down Han Kyung Wook and Lee Cheol Jin.

00:06:28.621 --> 00:06:31.541
You drive then.

00:06:31.541 --> 00:06:34.252
- You just ride along and complain nonstop. - The road is wide open,

00:06:34.252 --> 00:06:36.129
- so why aren't you speeding up? - You really talk too much.

00:06:36.129 --> 00:06:38.873
- Can't you just go? Step on it! - Jeez, seriously...

00:06:55.231 --> 00:06:57.734
You left so confidently, so why did you come back?

00:06:57.734 --> 00:06:59.652
Back then, I had a lot on my mind.

00:06:59.652 --> 00:07:02.197
It won't happen again.

00:07:02.197 --> 00:07:04.324
You're back, that's enough.

00:07:04.324 --> 00:07:06.076
There's someone who hasn't come back, after all.

00:07:06.076 --> 00:07:08.828
Hey, I'm back!

00:07:08.828 --> 00:07:10.663
Boss!

00:07:10.663 --> 00:07:11.706
I'm sorry, Gong Bok.

00:07:11.706 --> 00:07:13.166
- I'm a bit late. - What?

00:07:13.166 --> 00:07:15.210
You didn't bring Hwang Hwa San with you, did you?

00:07:15.210 --> 00:07:17.003
Here he goes again.

00:07:17.003 --> 00:07:18.713
Kang Beom Ryong.

00:07:18.713 --> 00:07:19.964
Have you decided which side you're on?

00:07:19.964 --> 00:07:23.927
Well, yeah, I'm the owner of the so-called 'Friendly Convenience Store.'

00:07:23.927 --> 00:07:28.056
I can't just ignore my local customers getting beaten.

00:07:28.056 --> 00:07:30.975
I'm sorry, Gong Bok, that you can't go back to the Hwasan faction.

00:07:30.975 --> 00:07:34.354
Didn't I say I'd follow you wherever you go?

00:07:34.354 --> 00:07:36.856
If this is the path you chose,

00:07:36.856 --> 00:07:38.933
I'll follow without hesitation.

00:07:40.944 --> 00:07:42.645
Sorry.

00:07:45.115 --> 00:07:47.283
You two are acting like you're filming a movie or something.

00:07:47.283 --> 00:07:49.953
Why did you run out if things are going to be like this?

00:07:49.953 --> 00:07:52.655
You guys just left like that, and Jeong Ho...

00:07:53.540 --> 00:07:56.909
Do you know how worried Jeong Ho Myung was?

00:07:57.752 --> 00:07:59.587
Really?

00:07:59.587 --> 00:08:03.174
I was about to feel hurt. Was that how it was, Mr. Jeong?

00:08:03.174 --> 00:08:07.220
I just said that because I was worried the plan would fall apart.

00:08:07.220 --> 00:08:08.680
Anyway, since things have turned out this way,

00:08:08.680 --> 00:08:10.932
We'll take care of Han Kyung Wook, and we'll take care of your boss too.

00:08:10.932 --> 00:08:12.142
So don't say anything else from now on.

00:08:12.142 --> 00:08:15.436
Yeah, I must stop our big boss from going the wrong way.

00:08:15.436 --> 00:08:17.105
What do we do first?

00:08:17.105 --> 00:08:19.899
Should we deal with those spies this guy was tailing first?

00:08:19.899 --> 00:08:22.152
Those guys are hiding at a tourist hotel

00:08:22.152 --> 00:08:23.653
On the outskirts of Yeongseondo Island.

00:08:23.653 --> 00:08:26.322
Perfect. Now that our powerhouse is here.

00:08:26.322 --> 00:08:27.323
Should we go right away?

00:08:27.323 --> 00:08:29.284
- Let's go, let's go! - No.

00:08:29.284 --> 00:08:31.411
The election is right around the corner.

00:08:31.411 --> 00:08:33.872
Even if we deal with Lee Cheol Jin,

00:08:33.872 --> 00:08:37.083
If Han Kyung Wook gets elected, it's all over.

00:08:37.083 --> 00:08:40.003
We don't even know when the code on the item will be cracked.

00:08:40.003 --> 00:08:42.881
We need to make our move before it's too late.

00:08:42.881 --> 00:08:44.340
Our big move?

00:08:44.340 --> 00:08:47.626
You need bait to catch a big fish.

00:08:49.929 --> 00:08:55.143
We'll use Lee Cheol Jin as bait to catch Han Kyung Wook.

00:08:55.143 --> 00:08:56.728
Lee Cheol Jin as bait?

00:08:56.728 --> 00:08:59.680
I've already called in reinforcements to help us.

00:08:59.680 --> 00:09:04.296
[Yeongseon Passenger Terminal]

00:09:04.296 --> 00:09:06.905
[Temporary Boarding and Alighting Zone]

00:09:06.905 --> 00:09:08.198
Yeah, don't worry.

00:09:08.198 --> 00:09:09.282
We're tailing her properly.

00:09:09.282 --> 00:09:12.952
I approved Prosecutor Kang's leave on purpose.

00:09:12.952 --> 00:09:15.246
You know things got worse because you lost her

00:09:15.246 --> 00:09:17.165
During her last vacation, right?

00:09:17.165 --> 00:09:20.951
This time, it's not surveillance. It's elimination.

00:09:22.170 --> 00:09:23.838
You absolutely cannot make a mistake.

00:09:23.838 --> 00:09:26.299
Yes, sir. This time, we'll make sure it's done.

00:09:26.299 --> 00:09:28.208
Yes, sir. Talk soon.

00:09:30.178 --> 00:09:32.764
That old man is really breathing down our necks.

00:09:32.764 --> 00:09:33.848
Ugh, so annoying.

00:09:33.848 --> 00:09:36.392
But are we really allowed to take out a prosecutor?

00:09:36.392 --> 00:09:38.603
Won't there be a problem?

00:09:38.603 --> 00:09:40.013
What problem could there be?

00:09:40.013 --> 00:09:43.274
The chief prosecutor of Criminal Affairs Division has our back.

00:09:43.274 --> 00:09:46.152
Stop worrying about useless things and just do our job properly this time.

00:09:46.152 --> 00:09:49.063
I'm sick and tired of following Prosecutor Kang around.

00:09:51.112 --> 00:09:52.200
Huh? She got in.

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:53.284
- Let's go quickly! - Yeah.

00:09:53.284 --> 00:09:55.328
Let's go. Let's get moving.

00:09:55.328 --> 00:09:57.738
Where is she going again this time?

00:09:59.207 --> 00:10:00.667
Oh, that startled me!

00:10:00.667 --> 00:10:02.293
- What is it? - What is it?

00:10:02.293 --> 00:10:03.795
That's strange.

00:10:03.795 --> 00:10:06.422
- Why? Did something explode? - Over here, sir!

00:10:06.422 --> 00:10:08.540
- What? - Why is this happening?

00:10:09.717 --> 00:10:11.386
This is driving me crazy!

00:10:11.386 --> 00:10:14.097
Prosecutor Kang is leaving. Do something about it!

00:10:14.097 --> 00:10:15.723
The tire is completely blown.

00:10:15.723 --> 00:10:17.934
That old man is going to lose his mind.

00:10:17.934 --> 00:10:21.980
It's my first time meeting you in person, but strangely, it doesn't feel awkward.

00:10:21.980 --> 00:10:24.315
Is it because I owe you some favors?

00:10:24.315 --> 00:10:27.193
I wouldn't call it owing me a favor or anything.

00:10:27.193 --> 00:10:29.862
I just pulled a few little tricks.

00:10:29.862 --> 00:10:33.533
Calling it a little trick is selling yourself short.

00:10:33.533 --> 00:10:39.163
You helped me shake off those annoying guys several times, naturally.

00:10:39.163 --> 00:10:40.206
I wanted to thank you.

00:10:40.206 --> 00:10:43.167
You can thank me later.

00:10:43.167 --> 00:10:47.714
Because I think I'll have to ask you for a pretty difficult favor.

00:10:47.714 --> 00:10:49.048
- A difficult favor? - Yes.

00:10:49.048 --> 00:10:50.550
I'm so excited. What is it?

00:10:50.550 --> 00:10:54.086
You'll find out when you get there. Everyone's waiting for you, ma'am.

00:11:17.618 --> 00:11:19.320
Prosecutor Kang?

00:11:20.788 --> 00:11:23.115
Have you been well, Mr. Bong Jae Soon?

00:11:28.463 --> 00:11:30.381
Well, I'm sure you've all heard,

00:11:30.381 --> 00:11:32.258
But things aren't looking good right now.

00:11:32.258 --> 00:11:34.120
North Korean agents have crossed down here,

00:11:34.120 --> 00:11:36.679
And with Hwang Hwa San joining Heaven Capital,

00:11:36.679 --> 00:11:38.556
Their development plans are moving faster.

00:11:38.556 --> 00:11:40.391
The victims of Heaven Capital's debt collection

00:11:40.391 --> 00:11:43.880
Are also preparing a protest in response.

00:11:43.880 --> 00:11:44.979
And the worst part is that...

00:11:44.979 --> 00:11:47.940
We don't know when the code on that item will be cracked.

00:11:47.940 --> 00:11:49.484
Exactly.

00:11:49.484 --> 00:11:53.529
We can't just sit around waiting for the code to be hacked.

00:11:53.529 --> 00:11:57.691
We need to find another way before Han Kyung Wook gets elected.

00:11:59.243 --> 00:12:03.373
Are you still being followed, Ms. Kang?

00:12:03.373 --> 00:12:07.960
Yes, everywhere I go, detectives stick to me like leeches,

00:12:07.960 --> 00:12:10.296
So it's not easy for me to move around.

00:12:10.296 --> 00:12:13.299
Jeong Ho Myung, even the prosecutor can't move around that easily.

00:12:13.299 --> 00:12:16.552
Do you think you can catch Han Kyung Wook with Lee Cheol Jin or whatever his name is?

00:12:16.552 --> 00:12:18.504
If you're planning to expose the connection

00:12:18.504 --> 00:12:20.348
Between Lee Cheol Jin and Han Kyung Wook, forget it.

00:12:20.348 --> 00:12:22.683
- Why? - Lee Cheol Jin and those agents

00:12:22.683 --> 00:12:27.397
Probably created fake identities as people with no family ties before operating here.

00:12:27.397 --> 00:12:30.650
Even if we catch them, confirming their identities alone would take months.

00:12:30.650 --> 00:12:33.319
By then, the game will already be over.

00:12:33.319 --> 00:12:37.156
Unless they walk around announcing "We're spies" themselves,

00:12:37.156 --> 00:12:39.742
Using Lee Cheol Jin is impossible.

00:12:39.742 --> 00:12:40.743
You know a lot about this, huh?

00:12:40.743 --> 00:12:42.736
Well, that's because I...

00:12:47.166 --> 00:12:49.168
Mr. Bong Jae Soon is right.

00:12:49.168 --> 00:12:52.463
Even if we catch Lee Cheol Jin, it means nothing if we can't link him

00:12:52.463 --> 00:12:53.923
To Han Kyung Wook.

00:12:53.923 --> 00:12:56.676
You just need to find it.

00:12:56.676 --> 00:12:58.302
- Gong Bok. - Yes?

00:12:58.302 --> 00:13:00.138
Check the CCTV footage

00:13:00.138 --> 00:13:03.433
And find out the location of the detectives following Ms. Kang.

00:13:03.433 --> 00:13:05.560
Oh, yes.

00:13:05.560 --> 00:13:09.564
And Ms. Kang, do you happen to know any reporters?

00:13:09.564 --> 00:13:13.317
Someone who can write a powerful article as quickly as possible.

00:13:13.317 --> 00:13:15.602
Powerful impact?

00:13:16.404 --> 00:13:17.655
Does it have to be a reporter?

00:13:17.655 --> 00:13:21.868
As long as we can draw people's attention, it doesn't have to be a reporter.

00:13:21.868 --> 00:13:23.119
How about a NewTuber with a million subscribers?

00:13:23.119 --> 00:13:25.163
A NewTuber with a million subscribers?

00:13:25.163 --> 00:13:26.864
That's perfect.

00:13:27.957 --> 00:13:30.835
Alright, everyone listen carefully.

00:13:30.835 --> 00:13:32.462
From now on,

00:13:32.462 --> 00:13:34.088
We're going to use Lee Cheol Jin

00:13:34.088 --> 00:13:39.126
To tie together Hwang Hwa San, Chairman Do, and Han Kyung Wook,

00:13:40.553 --> 00:13:43.088
And take them all down in one shot.

00:13:45.850 --> 00:13:47.551
Mr. Bong Jae Soon!

00:13:48.519 --> 00:13:50.354
Ms. Kang.

00:13:50.354 --> 00:13:53.682
I heard you got all your memories back.

00:13:54.567 --> 00:13:57.603
Just like I suspected, you're not an ordinary person.

00:13:58.571 --> 00:14:01.273
I thought you'd at least call me once.

00:14:03.117 --> 00:14:04.818
Are you alright?

00:14:07.079 --> 00:14:08.780
Ms. Kang.

00:14:13.336 --> 00:14:15.922
I think you should stop at this point.

00:14:15.922 --> 00:14:17.507
Stop what?

00:14:17.507 --> 00:14:20.051
Your feelings toward me.

00:14:20.051 --> 00:14:21.969
Pardon?

00:14:21.969 --> 00:14:28.434
I know, I know. I know feelings aren't something you can control.

00:14:28.434 --> 00:14:31.553
And besides, I'm also...

00:14:32.188 --> 00:14:33.898
Yes, that's right.

00:14:33.898 --> 00:14:36.275
I know forgetting won't be easy, but still, Ms. Kang,

00:14:36.275 --> 00:14:38.778
You need to get a hold of your feelings.

00:14:38.778 --> 00:14:42.773
Are you saying I've fallen for you or something, Mr. Bong Jae Soon?

00:14:45.451 --> 00:14:47.152
Oh, no.

00:15:18.484 --> 00:15:23.948
Sergeant Kim said once the protest starts, Heaven Capital will move in aggressively.

00:15:23.948 --> 00:15:26.826
They won't care if people get hurt or not.

00:15:26.826 --> 00:15:29.912
The protest is tomorrow. There's no way to stop it?

00:15:29.912 --> 00:15:32.832
I mean, what's the point in stopping it?

00:15:32.832 --> 00:15:34.625
We should just hold placards and fight with them.

00:15:34.625 --> 00:15:35.710
Are you crazy?

00:15:35.710 --> 00:15:37.461
It's not like it was made for hitting people.

00:15:37.461 --> 00:15:39.046
I don't care anymore.

00:15:39.046 --> 00:15:41.512
I just want to go back to my restaurant.

00:15:41.512 --> 00:15:43.217
I haven't worked the wok for so long

00:15:43.217 --> 00:15:45.416
My hands are going stiff.

00:15:45.416 --> 00:15:49.390
Protest or whatever, can we just go back

00:15:49.390 --> 00:15:51.058
And reopen the restaurant?

00:15:51.058 --> 00:15:53.728
- Dad! - Come on.

00:15:53.728 --> 00:15:56.424
People in the neighborhood could get hurt,

00:15:56.424 --> 00:15:57.815
You can't just watch like it's someone else's problem.

00:15:57.815 --> 00:16:00.443
If we don't watch, what other option do we even have?

00:16:00.443 --> 00:16:04.238
We don't have time, and there's no way we can handle this ourselves.

00:16:04.238 --> 00:16:06.198
Honestly, isn't this all over already?

00:16:06.198 --> 00:16:08.492
There is a way.

00:16:08.492 --> 00:16:09.619
Ms. Kang!

00:16:09.619 --> 00:16:12.997
It's been a while. Hello.

00:16:12.997 --> 00:16:14.665
Before the protest breaks out,

00:16:14.665 --> 00:16:18.544
There's a way to immobilize Han Kyung Wook and those Heaven Capital guys.

00:16:18.544 --> 00:16:21.413
So could you help out?

00:16:41.359 --> 00:16:44.654
Ms. Kang has already handled things at the hotel.

00:16:44.654 --> 00:16:48.532
Just carry out your assigned roles properly. Don't be nervous.

00:16:48.532 --> 00:16:50.868
- Yes. - Got it.

00:16:50.868 --> 00:16:51.786
- Don't be nervous. - Yeah.

00:16:51.786 --> 00:16:53.621
Then everyone, go to your assigned positions.

00:16:53.621 --> 00:16:55.864
- Let's go. - Alright, let's go!

00:17:06.842 --> 00:17:09.544
Where are they?

00:17:15.101 --> 00:17:17.344
Here they are.

00:17:22.817 --> 00:17:24.944
Yes, I found them, Ms. Kang.

00:17:24.944 --> 00:17:28.188
The detectives are at Yeongseon Intersection.

00:17:31.075 --> 00:17:34.829
It's like finding a needle in a haystack.

00:17:34.829 --> 00:17:37.748
Let's just give up.

00:17:37.748 --> 00:17:39.709
Are you telling me to report we lost her again?

00:17:39.709 --> 00:17:41.752
If this goes wrong,

00:17:41.752 --> 00:17:43.879
You and I are both done for.

00:17:43.879 --> 00:17:46.757
Stop complaining and just look for her! Seriously...

00:17:46.757 --> 00:17:50.052
You didn't think Prosecutor Kang would actually show up... But she did.

00:17:50.052 --> 00:17:51.345
- Where? - Over there, there.

00:17:51.345 --> 00:17:53.097
The convenience store!

00:17:53.097 --> 00:17:55.182
Oh? She's there! Oh! It's done, it's done.

00:17:55.182 --> 00:17:57.727
I told you she'd be here earlier.

00:17:57.727 --> 00:17:59.103
- It's done, it's done! - She got in, she got in!

00:17:59.103 --> 00:18:00.104
- Look! - She got in!

00:18:00.104 --> 00:18:02.064
Let's go.

00:18:02.064 --> 00:18:04.734
I've got you, I've got you!

00:18:04.734 --> 00:18:06.318
Is it this way? It's that way.

00:18:06.318 --> 00:18:08.571
<i>How is the progress on securing the item?</i>

00:18:08.571 --> 00:18:10.239
It's going smoothly.

00:18:10.239 --> 00:18:11.699
<i>We don't have much time.</i>

00:18:11.699 --> 00:18:14.452
You know the election is right around the corner.

00:18:14.452 --> 00:18:16.370
I told you it's in progress!

00:18:16.370 --> 00:18:17.663
<i>If it's really difficult,</i>

00:18:17.663 --> 00:18:20.699
Ask Chairman Hwang Hwa San and Chairman Do for help.

00:18:22.376 --> 00:18:26.172
You still don't know what those punks are plotting.

00:18:26.172 --> 00:18:27.339
<i>What do you mean?</i>

00:18:27.339 --> 00:18:31.302
Something about those two didn't sit right with me, so I looked into it.

00:18:31.302 --> 00:18:34.180
I'll send you the documents, so you can see for yourself.

00:18:34.180 --> 00:18:37.433
And I'll handle the item myself,

00:18:37.433 --> 00:18:40.510
So stop pushing me, okay?

00:18:44.023 --> 00:18:47.359
We outnumber them. How did we lose to those two?

00:18:47.359 --> 00:18:48.903
Get yourselves together quickly.

00:18:48.903 --> 00:18:51.572
We need to retrieve the item before Mr. Han finds out.

00:18:51.572 --> 00:18:53.273
- Yes, sir! - Yes, sir!

00:19:14.637 --> 00:19:16.889
Oh, sorry, sir.

00:19:16.889 --> 00:19:19.560
There's water leaking from the ceiling of the bathroom downstairs,

00:19:19.560 --> 00:19:20.893
Causing quite a fuss.

00:19:20.893 --> 00:19:23.521
May I take a quick look at the restroom?

00:19:23.521 --> 00:19:25.564
Why is water leaking?

00:19:25.564 --> 00:19:27.149
Then you should move to another room.

00:19:27.149 --> 00:19:29.735
We've got a group of guests right now.

00:19:29.735 --> 00:19:33.230
So it's fully occupied. It'll be resolved quickly.

00:19:34.615 --> 00:19:37.201
Oh, will it really be quick?

00:19:37.201 --> 00:19:38.744
Of course, of course.

00:19:38.744 --> 00:19:42.739
Mr. Cho here from the hardware store is a real professional.

00:19:44.708 --> 00:19:47.545
It'll only take 3 minutes, 3 minutes.

00:19:47.545 --> 00:19:50.956
No point making a scene, just finish quickly.

00:19:51.590 --> 00:19:54.134
Then please make it quick.

00:19:54.134 --> 00:19:55.427
Oh! Yes, yes, yes.

00:19:55.427 --> 00:19:58.848
- Three minutes. - Yes, thank you, thank you.

00:19:58.848 --> 00:20:00.933
I'll extend your check-out time when you leave.

00:20:00.933 --> 00:20:03.843
Thank you, thank you!

00:20:14.071 --> 00:20:15.772
Thank you!

00:20:21.120 --> 00:20:23.998
Wow, what a perfect spot to die.

00:20:23.998 --> 00:20:26.375
Let's go before we lose her again, sir.

00:20:26.375 --> 00:20:29.077
Let's go.

00:20:38.637 --> 00:20:40.338
It's this way, right?

00:20:49.440 --> 00:20:51.725
Who are these guys?

00:20:54.570 --> 00:20:55.696
Why are they here?

00:20:55.696 --> 00:20:57.698
What's going on?

00:20:57.698 --> 00:20:59.950
- What's this? - What is it?

00:20:59.950 --> 00:21:01.660
Yes? What is it?

00:21:01.660 --> 00:21:02.912
Yes, excuse us for a moment.

00:21:02.912 --> 00:21:04.296
Are you detectives from Imcheon station

00:21:04.296 --> 00:21:06.498
- here for support? - Support?

00:21:06.498 --> 00:21:09.543
We received a report that armed North Korean infiltrators are holding hostages here.

00:21:09.543 --> 00:21:11.211
Didn't you come to provide support?

00:21:11.211 --> 00:21:13.464
- Armed infiltrators? - It's an emergency, there's no time.

00:21:13.464 --> 00:21:15.382
Get out of the vehicle now.

00:21:15.382 --> 00:21:18.209
- Wait, wait, wait. - Get out now.

00:21:23.515 --> 00:21:24.934
Alright, alright.

00:21:24.934 --> 00:21:27.895
Everyone, don't panic. You can do it, right?

00:21:27.895 --> 00:21:32.349
We have to. We were told we could get the house back without a protest.

00:21:34.902 --> 00:21:36.111
Right, right.

00:21:36.111 --> 00:21:37.905
Float like a butterfly,

00:21:37.905 --> 00:21:40.366
And sting like a bee!

00:21:40.366 --> 00:21:42.451
Shall we loosen up a bit for the first time in a while?

00:21:42.451 --> 00:21:44.495
Don't be nervous.

00:21:44.495 --> 00:21:47.206
You look nervous though.

00:21:47.206 --> 00:21:48.707
- Alright, come out. - No, wait a minute.

00:21:48.707 --> 00:21:50.334
Well...

00:21:50.334 --> 00:21:52.670
It's true that we came here for support, but...

00:21:52.670 --> 00:21:54.129
Be careful, be careful.

00:21:54.129 --> 00:21:55.339
- I'm sorry. - Careful.

00:21:55.339 --> 00:21:57.415
The situation is worse than expected.

00:21:58.217 --> 00:22:00.761
But will this really get that many views?

00:22:00.761 --> 00:22:04.098
- You know what matters for views? - What is it?

00:22:04.098 --> 00:22:06.183
It's all about clickbait.

00:22:06.183 --> 00:22:08.602
My views have been dropping lately.

00:22:08.602 --> 00:22:12.606
I was thinking I might need to break an arm again.

00:22:12.606 --> 00:22:15.484
If real spies show up, this'll hit ten million views.

00:22:15.484 --> 00:22:17.778
Wow, over ten million would really be great.

00:22:17.778 --> 00:22:19.738
- I'll start the livestream. - Yes.

00:22:19.738 --> 00:22:21.439
It's done.

00:22:22.199 --> 00:22:25.077
Hello everyone, this is Sweatstorm.

00:22:25.077 --> 00:22:27.496
How are you doing, my "Pposong" viewers?

00:22:27.496 --> 00:22:29.164
Today is a very important day.

00:22:29.164 --> 00:22:34.128
Do spies exist in this day and age or not? Yes, they do, here...

00:22:34.128 --> 00:22:37.006
<i>Yes, I received a tip that armed infiltrators are staging a protest today,</i>

00:22:37.006 --> 00:22:39.133
<i>and I've come to the scene.</i>

00:22:39.133 --> 00:22:41.635
Oh, what do you mean a lie? It's not.

00:22:41.635 --> 00:22:45.556
<i>I came here after receiving an urgent tip, I'm telling you.</i>

00:22:45.556 --> 00:22:47.349
<i>Wait, wait.</i>

00:22:47.349 --> 00:22:51.136
<i>Look, the police are all over the place.</i>

00:22:59.240 --> 00:23:02.322
I won't be long.

00:23:02.322 --> 00:23:05.034
Where's the leak coming from?

00:23:05.034 --> 00:23:06.160
Look, look over there!

00:23:06.160 --> 00:23:07.536
- Over there, over there! - Where?

00:23:07.536 --> 00:23:10.039
Someone's injured right now!

00:23:10.039 --> 00:23:11.707
- What are we going to do? - Sir!

00:23:11.707 --> 00:23:14.284
This is a big problem, oh no!

00:23:14.960 --> 00:23:16.462
- Chairman, blood! - Huh? Blood.

00:23:16.462 --> 00:23:18.088
- It's blood! Blood. - Quick, that...

00:23:18.088 --> 00:23:19.506
Huh?

00:23:19.506 --> 00:23:20.758
What do we do?

00:23:20.758 --> 00:23:24.803
There are armed infiltrators inside, and they're...

00:23:24.803 --> 00:23:26.430
These punks.

00:23:26.430 --> 00:23:29.384
Seems like they're going wild inside, darn it.

00:23:29.384 --> 00:23:33.437
Well, entering rashly might be dangerous.

00:23:33.437 --> 00:23:34.438
- Detectives. - Yes?

00:23:34.438 --> 00:23:35.814
You've negotiated before, haven't you?

00:23:35.814 --> 00:23:37.357
N-Negotiation?

00:23:37.357 --> 00:23:40.694
You're the only ones we can trust here.

00:23:40.694 --> 00:23:42.404
Please take command of the scene.

00:23:42.404 --> 00:23:44.031
- We, we... - Excuse me, here!

00:23:44.031 --> 00:23:45.949
Give the detectives a megaphone, megaphone!

00:23:45.949 --> 00:23:47.117
Oh, megaphone!

00:23:47.117 --> 00:23:48.911
Quick, to the hospital, hospital!

00:23:48.911 --> 00:23:51.497
- It hurts! - The hospital!

00:23:51.497 --> 00:23:53.332
Sir, this...

00:23:53.332 --> 00:23:55.292
Megaphone, megaphone!

00:23:55.292 --> 00:23:56.585
Sir!

00:23:56.585 --> 00:23:57.628
Right now, quickly!

00:23:57.628 --> 00:24:00.589
There are armed infiltrators here right now!

00:24:00.589 --> 00:24:02.216
I saw them, I'm telling you! From over there right now!

00:24:02.216 --> 00:24:05.594
Armed infiltrators, listen up!

00:24:05.594 --> 00:24:10.057
You're all surrounded right now!

00:24:10.057 --> 00:24:12.976
- Drop your weapons immediately, - Comrade Lieutenant!

00:24:12.976 --> 00:24:15.011
And surrender!

00:24:15.813 --> 00:24:18.315
I repeat!

00:24:18.315 --> 00:24:20.683
Listen, armed infiltrators!

00:24:20.683 --> 00:24:24.648
Drop your weapons.

00:24:24.648 --> 00:24:30.035
- And your lives will be spared! - Armed infiltrators?

00:24:30.035 --> 00:24:31.995
- Are they talking about us now? - We have no intention

00:24:31.995 --> 00:24:34.164
- I don't know. - of harming you.

00:24:34.164 --> 00:24:37.742
- I repeat! - Prepare yourselves. Let's take cover first.

00:24:38.585 --> 00:24:40.411
Stop right there!

00:24:41.213 --> 00:24:44.007
If even one of you moves,

00:24:44.007 --> 00:24:45.875
I'll throw this!

00:24:55.894 --> 00:24:58.021
- You punk... - I'll throw this!

00:24:58.021 --> 00:25:00.357
I'll really throw it!

00:25:00.357 --> 00:25:01.608
Who are you exactly?

00:25:01.608 --> 00:25:02.985
Me?

00:25:02.985 --> 00:25:05.487
I'm NIS Counterintelligence Team Leader, Cho Seong Wo.

00:25:05.487 --> 00:25:07.531
A spy hunter who catches spies like you.

00:25:07.531 --> 00:25:10.284
I've caught plenty of you.

00:25:10.284 --> 00:25:12.327
Oh!

00:25:12.327 --> 00:25:14.997
That punk from ten years ago who was after the item?

00:25:14.997 --> 00:25:17.791
Yeah, Lieutenant Lee Cheol Jin.

00:25:17.791 --> 00:25:20.460
Give up, you're not getting out of here.

00:25:20.460 --> 00:25:22.671
I already put it out there that there are armed infiltrators here.

00:25:22.671 --> 00:25:26.082
And what do you think the media will do? They'll go crazy.

00:25:27.759 --> 00:25:29.178
Right?

00:25:29.178 --> 00:25:32.598
You have two choices. First!

00:25:32.598 --> 00:25:33.807
Surrender and find redemption.

00:25:33.807 --> 00:25:37.144
Second, get dragged out like dogs by the military and police.

00:25:37.144 --> 00:25:39.938
Now think about it. What's better for you?

00:25:39.938 --> 00:25:41.389
Make a choice.

00:25:42.513 --> 00:25:45.896
[Hul Park]

00:25:55.720 --> 00:25:57.789
Oh, you...

00:25:57.789 --> 00:25:58.874
Hold on, hold on.

00:25:58.874 --> 00:26:00.334
Come this way, come this way.

00:26:00.334 --> 00:26:04.755
Okay, these are the heroes who caught spies with nothing but their bare hands.

00:26:04.755 --> 00:26:07.674
- Give them a round of applause! - Applause, applause, applause!

00:26:07.674 --> 00:26:09.051
Wow, the comments are going wild.

00:26:09.051 --> 00:26:10.552
Say a few words to the viewers here.

00:26:10.552 --> 00:26:12.095
- Hello. - What, Pposong, Pposong?

00:26:12.095 --> 00:26:14.056
- Pposong! - Stop filming now, stop.

00:26:14.056 --> 00:26:16.350
- Stop filming. - Wow, fighting!

00:26:16.350 --> 00:26:17.476
I said stop filming!

00:26:17.476 --> 00:26:19.436
- Oh, this is chaos. - Let's go quickly, sir.

00:26:19.436 --> 00:26:21.772
- You've worked hard. - Oh, you scared me!

00:26:21.772 --> 00:26:23.899
You caught all the spies.

00:26:23.899 --> 00:26:27.644
Guess following me around was worth it.

00:26:29.112 --> 00:26:30.280
So how did it go?

00:26:30.280 --> 00:26:33.951
It went according to plan. As soon as we got Lee Cheol Jin's confession,

00:26:33.951 --> 00:26:36.119
I'll make sure a warrant is issued for every one

00:26:36.119 --> 00:26:38.830
Of Han Kyung Wook's men so none of them get away.

00:26:38.830 --> 00:26:41.166
Well, it won't be easy to get them approved,

00:26:41.166 --> 00:26:42.417
But we'll have to take drastic measures.

00:26:42.417 --> 00:26:45.712
<i>Yes, then we'll gather them all</i>

00:26:45.712 --> 00:26:49.383
So we can arrest them as soon as you bring the warrants.

00:26:49.383 --> 00:26:53.178
Please come here tomorrow by 6 PM with the warrants

00:26:53.178 --> 00:26:54.471
And full manpower.

00:26:54.471 --> 00:26:59.017
But will it be possible to lure Han Kyung Wook at the right time?

00:26:59.017 --> 00:27:02.312
The election is the day after Yeongseondo Island's campaign.

00:27:02.312 --> 00:27:06.441
Tomorrow is the only chance we have to lure and catch him.

00:27:06.441 --> 00:27:08.986
I'll somehow try to lure him,

00:27:08.986 --> 00:27:12.781
So please make sure the preparations are thorough, Ms. Kang.

00:27:12.781 --> 00:27:14.482
Yes.

00:27:19.121 --> 00:27:24.167
So Prosecutor Kang caught Lee Cheol Jin?

00:27:24.167 --> 00:27:25.419
Yeah.

00:27:25.419 --> 00:27:27.587
With this much attention,

00:27:27.587 --> 00:27:31.008
Lee Cheol Jin knows he can't just back out now.

00:27:31.008 --> 00:27:32.801
If he wants to live, he'll confess something.

00:27:32.801 --> 00:27:35.637
Alright, let's say everything up to here went according to your plan.

00:27:35.637 --> 00:27:36.722
What about next?

00:27:36.722 --> 00:27:38.473
We've got Han Kyung Wook, Chairman Do, and even our big boss all here.

00:27:38.473 --> 00:27:42.227
And you're thinking of arresting them all in one go. Is that really possible?

00:27:42.227 --> 00:27:45.939
If we use the item as bait, it's definitely possible.

00:27:45.939 --> 00:27:49.735
With Lee Cheol Jin captured and the item exposed, it'll be a fatal blow.

00:27:49.735 --> 00:27:51.737
Han Kyung Wook will have no choice but to come.

00:27:51.737 --> 00:27:54.740
And Hwang Hwa San will also need the item to move against him.

00:27:54.740 --> 00:27:59.077
But do we really have to gather everyone and take them down at once?

00:27:59.077 --> 00:28:03.457
If even one of them escapes, the project could still proceed.

00:28:03.457 --> 00:28:07.836
We have to strike all at once before they notice.

00:28:07.836 --> 00:28:09.629
But still, isn't that a bit...

00:28:09.629 --> 00:28:12.049
What? Got a problem?

00:28:12.049 --> 00:28:15.177
What if Prosecutor Kang can't make it on time?

00:28:15.177 --> 00:28:19.380
We'd have to hold out on our own. Would that even be possible?

00:28:24.186 --> 00:28:27.930
It wouldn't be possible.

00:28:29.107 --> 00:28:30.400
What?

00:28:30.400 --> 00:28:35.354
We just need to stall until Prosecutor Kang arrives.

00:28:39.826 --> 00:28:42.153
We go with guerrilla tactics.

00:28:59.054 --> 00:29:00.838
Why aren't you sleeping?

00:29:05.936 --> 00:29:08.846
It's tomorrow. How could I possibly sleep?

00:29:14.361 --> 00:29:16.571
You haven't slept either?

00:29:16.571 --> 00:29:19.908
What, you're both here?

00:29:19.908 --> 00:29:21.535
Where's Gong Bok?

00:29:21.535 --> 00:29:23.120
He passed out earlier.

00:29:23.120 --> 00:29:26.248
Wow, even though he's the most worried,

00:29:26.248 --> 00:29:28.417
He still sleeps well, huh?

00:29:28.417 --> 00:29:32.578
At least he should sleep well. We don't even know what tomorrow will bring.

00:29:38.260 --> 00:29:40.387
Jeong Ho Myung.

00:29:40.387 --> 00:29:41.888
Be honest with me.

00:29:41.888 --> 00:29:47.927
What do you think our chances of success are tomorrow?

00:29:50.939 --> 00:29:53.850
If we're lucky,

00:29:55.402 --> 00:29:57.487
- I'd say about fifty percent. - Come on.

00:29:57.487 --> 00:30:00.949
Our lives are on the line, and it's only fifty-fifty?

00:30:00.949 --> 00:30:03.401
That's already being generous.

00:30:18.049 --> 00:30:20.209
When I was an agent,

00:30:21.636 --> 00:30:24.973
I never even thought about failure

00:30:24.973 --> 00:30:28.018
Before a life-or-death operation.

00:30:28.018 --> 00:30:32.022
I just kept thinking positive thoughts

00:30:32.022 --> 00:30:34.941
About what we'd do if it succeeded.

00:30:34.941 --> 00:30:40.188
And surprisingly, that actually helped.

00:30:41.323 --> 00:30:44.493
Who hasn't been on a mission before? Don't act like you're new to this.

00:30:44.493 --> 00:30:47.403
If this operation succeeds,

00:30:48.580 --> 00:30:49.998
I'm going to watch a movie.

00:30:49.998 --> 00:30:51.416
No one asked though.

00:30:51.416 --> 00:30:52.459
A movie?

00:30:52.459 --> 00:30:54.628
Yeah, a movie.

00:30:54.628 --> 00:30:57.255
I'm going to ask her to watch that Chow Yun Fat movie together,

00:30:57.255 --> 00:31:01.092
Since we missed it last time.

00:31:01.092 --> 00:31:04.095
All you plan to do if we survive is watch a movie?

00:31:04.095 --> 00:31:06.973
What's wrong with a movie? So, what great thing are you going to do?

00:31:06.973 --> 00:31:08.767
Me?

00:31:08.767 --> 00:31:11.770
If I get the diamonds,

00:31:11.770 --> 00:31:14.898
I'll go to Monaco with Nam Il.

00:31:14.898 --> 00:31:17.859
I figure seeing another world

00:31:17.859 --> 00:31:21.112
Might help him grow up a bit.

00:31:21.112 --> 00:31:26.952
Oh, so basically, it's just a family trip for you, huh?

00:31:26.952 --> 00:31:28.495
Jeong Ho Myung,

00:31:28.495 --> 00:31:30.372
Do you have any different plans?

00:31:30.372 --> 00:31:34.668
Well, I don't have anything special either.

00:31:34.668 --> 00:31:40.706
I just want to take a photo to hang in the restaurant.

00:31:41.633 --> 00:31:46.137
As a symbol of a new start for the rest of my life.

00:31:46.137 --> 00:31:48.130
With the whole family.

00:31:52.561 --> 00:31:55.647
Once we truly wrap this up,

00:31:55.647 --> 00:31:58.775
Can we really start over the way we want?

00:31:58.775 --> 00:32:00.318
Why couldn't we?

00:32:00.318 --> 00:32:02.737
We're only halfway through life.

00:32:02.737 --> 00:32:08.484
I'll go all in and give it everything I've got for the rest of my life.

00:32:09.494 --> 00:32:11.988
If this succeeds, you better give me the diamonds, okay?

00:32:40.840 --> 00:32:42.312
[2 Han Kyung Wook]

00:32:50.201 --> 00:32:52.570
This is the material secured by Lee Cheol Jin.

00:32:54.789 --> 00:32:57.542
We checked the voice recordings too,

00:32:57.542 --> 00:32:59.753
And it's confirmed Chairman Do and Hwang Hwa San betrayed us.

00:32:59.753 --> 00:33:03.205
They're all getting on my nerves right before a major move.

00:33:04.591 --> 00:33:06.635
I'll take care of it once the election ends.

00:33:06.635 --> 00:33:09.220
Tell Lee Cheol Jin to keep checking.

00:33:09.220 --> 00:33:14.842
But, since yesterday, Lee Cheol Jin has gone dark.

00:33:16.353 --> 00:33:18.521
Yes, glad to meet you. I'm candidate number 2.

00:33:18.521 --> 00:33:19.856
Yes, thank you.

00:33:19.856 --> 00:33:21.232
- Candidate number 2. - Candidate number 2.

00:33:21.232 --> 00:33:23.068
[2 Han Kyung Wook] Yes, I'm Han Kyung Wook.

00:33:23.068 --> 00:33:24.653
- Thank you. - Please support candidate number 2.

00:33:24.653 --> 00:33:27.072
- Candidate, could I take a photo with you? - Yes, go ahead.

00:33:27.072 --> 00:33:28.406
- Alright. - Candidate number 2.

00:33:28.406 --> 00:33:30.983
- Thank you. - Yes, candidate number 2.

00:33:32.452 --> 00:33:33.495
Please vote for number 2.

00:33:33.495 --> 00:33:35.780
It's candidate number 2, number 2.

00:33:50.053 --> 00:33:53.556
What's wrong? You look like you've seen a ghost.

00:33:53.556 --> 00:33:55.257
No, it's nothing.

00:33:59.312 --> 00:34:00.772
- Well... - Huh?

00:34:00.772 --> 00:34:02.857
I got an urgent call from the campaign.

00:34:02.857 --> 00:34:04.234
Sir, please take a short break.

00:34:04.234 --> 00:34:06.236
We're in the middle of a rally!

00:34:06.236 --> 00:34:08.479
- Just be quick. - Yes, yes.

00:34:35.098 --> 00:34:37.225
Is it okay for you to leave your seat?

00:34:37.225 --> 00:34:39.644
The election is almost here.

00:34:39.644 --> 00:34:42.346
You should keep meeting voters.

00:34:48.361 --> 00:34:53.908
Seeing you smile so warmly like that,

00:34:53.908 --> 00:34:59.122
It really makes me realize how scary human greed is.

00:34:59.122 --> 00:35:01.532
You've completely lost your mind, huh?

00:35:02.333 --> 00:35:04.669
You've got the nerve to come find me yourself?

00:35:04.669 --> 00:35:07.380
You came to my restaurant to check in, didn't you?

00:35:07.380 --> 00:35:12.051
So I wanted to visit you once, showing respect as a junior.

00:35:12.051 --> 00:35:13.595
What are you plotting?

00:35:13.595 --> 00:35:15.221
Plotting?

00:35:15.221 --> 00:35:19.601
I just came to see your last moments, really.

00:35:19.601 --> 00:35:22.061
Once you're arrested,

00:35:22.061 --> 00:35:24.430
It'll be hard to see you again.

00:35:25.565 --> 00:35:27.734
Stop bluffing.

00:35:27.734 --> 00:35:31.362
You think I don't know the item is encrypted?

00:35:31.362 --> 00:35:35.825
Don't tell me you haven't heard yet?

00:35:35.825 --> 00:35:39.162
Oh, you must've been too busy to watch TV.

00:35:39.162 --> 00:35:43.541
Turn on the news. Something very interesting might be on.

00:35:43.541 --> 00:35:45.418
I should go watch it too.

00:35:45.418 --> 00:35:48.755
Well then, sir, we probably won't meet again,

00:35:48.755 --> 00:35:52.625
But I hope you live long and healthy and pay for your sins.

00:36:04.229 --> 00:36:05.605
Are you alright?

00:36:05.605 --> 00:36:06.940
Follow him quietly.

00:36:06.940 --> 00:36:09.818
Find out where he's hiding no matter what.

00:36:09.818 --> 00:36:11.018
Yes, sir.

00:36:16.157 --> 00:36:20.119
<i>One of the suspects has been identified as Lieutenant Lee Cheol Jin,</i>

00:36:20.119 --> 00:36:24.207
<i>a senior lieutenant in North Korea's Ministry of People's Armed Forces,</i>

00:36:24.207 --> 00:36:26.000
[Six spies implicated Han Kyung Wook] <i>and is accused of infiltrating the country,</i>

00:36:26.000 --> 00:36:29.170
<i>collecting classified information, and threatening public safety.</i>

00:36:29.170 --> 00:36:31.589
<i>We have obtained testimony</i>

00:36:31.589 --> 00:36:33.299
<i>that former Assemblyman Han Kyung Wook</i>

00:36:33.299 --> 00:36:38.012
<i>currently running for mayor of Imcheon City, is the key mastermind behind the case.</i>

00:36:38.012 --> 00:36:40.139
<i>I sincerely regret having to make this announcement</i>

00:36:40.139 --> 00:36:42.809
<i>at such a sensitive time, with the mayoral election</i>

00:36:42.809 --> 00:36:45.186
Just around the corner.

00:36:45.186 --> 00:36:49.482
However, as this is an urgent matter threatening national security,

00:36:49.482 --> 00:36:54.070
We, the prosecution, pledge to the public

00:36:54.070 --> 00:36:55.780
That we will fully and clearly

00:36:55.780 --> 00:36:58.950
Establish the truth of this case with complete transparency,

00:36:58.950 --> 00:37:02.528
Without any political bias or intent.

00:37:03.705 --> 00:37:06.249
We will send the location of the item you are looking for.

00:37:06.249 --> 00:37:08.075
Please come.

00:37:12.922 --> 00:37:14.748
You've done a great job.

00:37:17.343 --> 00:37:21.964
- You did provoke Han Kyung Wook on purpose? - I even gave away our location deliberately.

00:37:23.725 --> 00:37:27.511
Alright, let's get to it.

00:37:29.355 --> 00:37:31.983
Still, this is the day we finish the operation

00:37:31.983 --> 00:37:33.943
We failed ten years ago.

00:37:33.943 --> 00:37:36.645
We can't show up looking like this, right?

00:37:42.076 --> 00:37:46.238
Just for today, let's go back to that day ten years ago.

00:37:48.875 --> 00:37:50.576
It's not a skirt, right?

00:37:53.671 --> 00:37:56.090
We've confirmed their location.

00:37:56.090 --> 00:37:58.626
They're at Yeongseon Resort.

00:38:01.763 --> 00:38:03.097
What about the Rangers?

00:38:03.097 --> 00:38:04.682
They're ready.

00:38:04.682 --> 00:38:07.384
Our "lambs" have arrived as well.

00:38:08.311 --> 00:38:11.397
Mr. Hwang, as you're well aware,

00:38:11.397 --> 00:38:13.691
You must never let your guard down in times like these.

00:38:13.691 --> 00:38:16.894
They're not your average guys, huh?

00:38:17.528 --> 00:38:22.450
We need to prepare perfectly and strike decisively, okay?

00:38:22.450 --> 00:38:27.038
I'm more of an expert in this than you, Chairman Do.

00:38:27.038 --> 00:38:33.494
It'll all be over before they even realize they've been hit.

00:38:34.629 --> 00:38:39.300
Wasn't Prosecutor Kang supposed to be handled by you, Chief?

00:38:39.300 --> 00:38:44.180
Well, I was going to, but she just...

00:38:44.180 --> 00:38:47.225
Anyway, please give me some time.

00:38:47.225 --> 00:38:49.644
I'll do my best to block the warrants.

00:38:49.644 --> 00:38:52.146
You'll try your best?

00:38:52.146 --> 00:38:54.223
You call that an answer?

00:38:54.857 --> 00:38:57.443
Block them no matter what.

00:38:57.443 --> 00:38:59.112
If you can't stop this,

00:38:59.112 --> 00:39:01.572
I'm not the only one who'll go down.

00:39:01.572 --> 00:39:05.159
Are you threatening me right now?

00:39:05.159 --> 00:39:07.662
Isn't that obvious?

00:39:07.662 --> 00:39:13.033
I can't give you much time. Fix it today, no matter what.

00:39:14.711 --> 00:39:16.963
What on earth is happening right now?

00:39:16.963 --> 00:39:19.048
Is this a North Korea-related operation?

00:39:19.048 --> 00:39:21.592
Or did you actually do something yourself?

00:39:21.592 --> 00:39:24.554
Ah, forget it. How are you going to take responsibility for dragging

00:39:24.554 --> 00:39:25.972
North Korea into my image?

00:39:25.972 --> 00:39:28.182
Why don't you quiet down?

00:39:28.182 --> 00:39:29.726
I'm thinking right now.

00:39:29.726 --> 00:39:31.477
What?

00:39:31.477 --> 00:39:35.648
Han Kyung Wook! Why are you glaring like that?

00:39:35.648 --> 00:39:38.317
For someone who played around with those North Korean punks,

00:39:38.317 --> 00:39:40.519
You think you did well?

00:39:45.491 --> 00:39:46.993
Huh?

00:39:46.993 --> 00:39:49.829
Wait, Assemblyman Han, what's wrong with you?

00:39:49.829 --> 00:39:51.789
You're being really noisy.

00:39:51.789 --> 00:39:53.916
Kim Joong Hyuk!

00:39:53.916 --> 00:39:57.211
At least I got some money while dealing with those North Korean punks,

00:39:57.211 --> 00:40:00.757
But what did you get from fooling around with young girls?

00:40:00.757 --> 00:40:02.633
You even handed over a building.

00:40:02.633 --> 00:40:05.053
- Do your kids even know? - What?

00:40:05.053 --> 00:40:08.389
It wouldn't be hard to flood the internet with photos of you

00:40:08.389 --> 00:40:11.225
With girls young enough to be your daughter.

00:40:11.225 --> 00:40:13.061
- Huh? - What,

00:40:13.061 --> 00:40:16.397
Should I make you a national adulterer right now?

00:40:16.397 --> 00:40:19.484
What? Adultery? You...

00:40:19.484 --> 00:40:21.652
Kim Joong Hyuk.

00:40:21.652 --> 00:40:23.613
If I really wanted to,

00:40:23.613 --> 00:40:28.284
I could bury you without a trace, and no one would ever know.

00:40:28.284 --> 00:40:30.286
So if you don't want to die,

00:40:30.286 --> 00:40:33.581
Mobilize the prosecutors and the press and shut this down.

00:40:33.581 --> 00:40:35.374
Do you understand what I'm saying?

00:40:35.374 --> 00:40:37.868
Yeah, sure, sure.

00:41:20.336 --> 00:41:22.037
There's no one here.

00:41:22.672 --> 00:41:25.508
Did they catch on and run away?

00:41:25.508 --> 00:41:28.919
<i>There is no connection. Please leave a message...</i>

00:41:41.607 --> 00:41:44.810
Run away? Who's running away!

00:41:46.404 --> 00:41:48.197
We were just waiting right here.

00:41:48.197 --> 00:41:50.816
Hi, hi, hi!

00:41:51.492 --> 00:41:53.318
Wow, there are a lot of you.

00:41:54.287 --> 00:41:55.988
Big boss?

00:41:58.708 --> 00:42:00.209
Mr. Hwang!

00:42:00.209 --> 00:42:02.837
What's the situation here?

00:42:02.837 --> 00:42:05.256
Kang Beom Ryong, Ma Gong Bok!

00:42:05.256 --> 00:42:08.584
You dare betray me?

00:42:09.969 --> 00:42:12.305
Do you even have the right to say that, boss?

00:42:12.305 --> 00:42:14.140
What did you say?

00:42:14.140 --> 00:42:16.225
You said you'd only take the item.

00:42:16.225 --> 00:42:19.395
But you've brought all your men.

00:42:19.395 --> 00:42:22.899
You were planning to take out Ma Gong Bok and Kang Beom Ryong

00:42:22.899 --> 00:42:24.150
Once you got the item, weren't you?

00:42:24.150 --> 00:42:25.735
You NIS punk!

00:42:25.735 --> 00:42:26.736
You...

00:42:26.736 --> 00:42:27.737
Mr. Hwang.

00:42:27.737 --> 00:42:29.822
Calm down, calm down.

00:42:29.822 --> 00:42:33.201
Alright everyone, let's calm down

00:42:33.201 --> 00:42:35.286
And have a little talk.

00:42:35.286 --> 00:42:40.249
I've heard a bit about what happened with you guys ten years ago.

00:42:40.249 --> 00:42:42.919
So, the conclusion is

00:42:42.919 --> 00:42:46.339
You want revenge on Han Kyung Wook, right?

00:42:46.339 --> 00:42:49.800
That's right! We're the same, same, yeah?

00:42:49.800 --> 00:42:53.179
We've got something to settle with Han Kyung Wook too, okay?

00:42:53.179 --> 00:42:55.514
Hey, foreigner!

00:42:55.514 --> 00:42:58.017
So what are you going to do about it?

00:42:58.017 --> 00:42:59.894
Well, anyway,

00:42:59.894 --> 00:43:05.107
The four of you aren't exactly enough to handle Han Kyung Wook, right?

00:43:05.107 --> 00:43:06.943
So let's not waste our energy,

00:43:06.943 --> 00:43:08.945
Hand the item over to us.

00:43:08.945 --> 00:43:13.491
And we'll make sure you get your revenge.

00:43:13.491 --> 00:43:15.192
Really?

00:43:19.997 --> 00:43:22.041
How did you end up here, Mr. Han?

00:43:22.041 --> 00:43:23.951
Mr. Han!

00:43:25.127 --> 00:43:28.923
Hyeon Tae, Do Hyeon Tae!

00:43:28.923 --> 00:43:32.176
I've told you before.

00:43:32.176 --> 00:43:35.763
Know your place and don't cross the line.

00:43:35.763 --> 00:43:40.351
I thought you had good judgment, Chairman Hwang.

00:43:40.351 --> 00:43:42.603
But I've misjudged you.

00:43:42.603 --> 00:43:43.980
I'm deeply disappointed.

00:43:43.980 --> 00:43:46.649
Disappointed, my foot.

00:43:46.649 --> 00:43:48.401
Maybe you're the one

00:43:48.401 --> 00:43:51.696
Who needs to know your place, Mr. Han Kyung Wook.

00:43:51.696 --> 00:43:54.407
- What? - Do you think we came this far

00:43:54.407 --> 00:43:57.317
Without preparing for this situation?

00:44:08.296 --> 00:44:14.167
Alright, well... I know you're all upset with me.

00:44:14.802 --> 00:44:20.007
But still, we shouldn't be fighting each other.

00:44:23.060 --> 00:44:26.805
Because that's exactly what he wants.

00:44:27.606 --> 00:44:29.433
Jeong Ho Myung.

00:44:30.067 --> 00:44:34.488
Looks like your plan is to make us fight each other

00:44:34.488 --> 00:44:39.076
And make us destroy each other.

00:44:39.076 --> 00:44:45.073
What do I do? I don't really plan to fight these two.

00:44:47.043 --> 00:44:48.836
What do you think?

00:44:48.836 --> 00:44:51.964
Rather than playing right into their hands,

00:44:51.964 --> 00:44:56.710
Let's deal with them first and talk it through calmly.

00:44:57.636 --> 00:44:58.763
Talk about what?

00:44:58.763 --> 00:45:05.061
Well, we could even talk about redistributing the profits from the project.

00:45:05.061 --> 00:45:09.440
There should be room for negotiation, don't you think?

00:45:09.440 --> 00:45:11.266
Do you believe that?

00:45:12.610 --> 00:45:16.188
Do you think Han Kyung Wook would negotiate with traitors?

00:45:27.541 --> 00:45:29.043
Fine.

00:45:29.043 --> 00:45:34.664
First, let's deal with the traitor Judas first.

00:45:37.510 --> 00:45:39.261
Ho Myung.

00:45:39.261 --> 00:45:42.473
As your senior, this is my final act of generosity.

00:45:42.473 --> 00:45:45.893
Hand over the item and back off quietly.

00:45:45.893 --> 00:45:49.596
Then, I'll spare your life.

00:45:55.986 --> 00:45:58.438
And what if I refuse?

00:46:01.283 --> 00:46:02.984
What are you all waiting for?

00:46:26.308 --> 00:46:28.009
Ma'am!

00:46:29.895 --> 00:46:33.274
We've got a problem. All the warrants got rejected.

00:46:33.274 --> 00:46:36.485
Ah... they got rejected?

00:46:36.485 --> 00:46:39.447
It seems like the Chief Prosecutor might have intervened.

00:46:39.447 --> 00:46:41.148
What should we do?

00:46:43.912 --> 00:46:48.040
[Yeongseon Resort]

00:47:14.940 --> 00:47:17.359
Oh, Prosecutor Kang!

00:47:17.359 --> 00:47:21.062
I was just about to call you, and you've come at the right time.

00:47:28.245 --> 00:47:29.371
What's going on?

00:47:29.371 --> 00:47:31.740
I saw your press conference.

00:47:55.481 --> 00:47:58.108
I also watched the press conference.

00:47:58.108 --> 00:48:04.231
Wow, you're even more beautiful in person than on TV.

00:48:05.658 --> 00:48:10.162
You don't really look like someone who catches spies.

00:48:10.162 --> 00:48:15.334
Come on, do you really think those guys are actual spies?

00:48:15.334 --> 00:48:22.312
Prosecutor Kang just made a fuss because she wanted attention.

00:48:22.312 --> 00:48:24.584
Right, Prosecutor Kang?

00:48:31.100 --> 00:48:34.344
- Are you alright? - No. Darn it!

00:49:10.764 --> 00:49:14.018
Aren't you ashamed at all, Chief?

00:49:14.018 --> 00:49:15.978
I'll give you one last chance.

00:49:15.978 --> 00:49:19.973
Proceed with the warrants properly.

00:49:29.366 --> 00:49:32.578
You know exactly who these guys are,

00:49:32.578 --> 00:49:35.539
Don't you, Prosecutor Kang?

00:49:35.539 --> 00:49:37.791
Make the right choice, okay?

00:49:37.791 --> 00:49:41.253
Depending on your choice,

00:49:41.253 --> 00:49:44.256
You could become a corrupt prosecutor

00:49:44.256 --> 00:49:47.301
Backing gangsters and spies!

00:49:47.301 --> 00:49:52.473
A prosecutor who has ties with gangsters and North Korea?

00:49:52.473 --> 00:49:57.385
When things get messy below, the higher-ups are the ones who suffer.

00:49:58.145 --> 00:50:00.773
This is embarrassing, sir.

00:50:00.773 --> 00:50:04.559
We should do a full cleanup soon.

00:50:19.875 --> 00:50:21.576
Boss!

00:50:34.723 --> 00:50:36.100
Gong Bok!

00:50:36.100 --> 00:50:38.560
What are you waiting for?

00:50:38.560 --> 00:50:40.813
Are you just going to stand there?

00:50:40.813 --> 00:50:43.649
I feel a bit reluctant to leave.

00:50:43.649 --> 00:50:46.402
There are a few people I want to introduce.

00:50:46.402 --> 00:50:49.521
- Introduce? - Come on in.

00:50:53.909 --> 00:50:55.119
Well, they're...

00:50:55.119 --> 00:50:56.912
You guys!

00:50:56.912 --> 00:50:59.289
Do you know them?

00:50:59.289 --> 00:51:03.669
Well, considering you've been making calls like this.

00:51:03.669 --> 00:51:07.131
<i>I approved Prosecutor Kang's leave on purpose.</i>

00:51:07.131 --> 00:51:09.383
<i>You know things got worse because you lost her</i>

00:51:09.383 --> 00:51:10.968
<i>during her last vacation, right?</i>

00:51:10.968 --> 00:51:14.263
<i>This time, it's not surveillance. It's elimination.</i>

00:51:14.263 --> 00:51:16.548
<i>You absolutely cannot make a mistake.</i>

00:51:21.979 --> 00:51:26.442
Make the right decision, both of you.

00:51:26.442 --> 00:51:30.946
These guys are conspirators who ordered the assassination of a Korean prosecutor!

00:51:30.946 --> 00:51:34.983
If you don't want to be swept away together with them.

00:51:36.200 --> 00:51:38.071
This way!

00:52:02.519 --> 00:52:04.220
Boss!

00:52:10.184 --> 00:52:13.238
Sorry, sorry, sorry, ugh.

00:52:13.238 --> 00:52:14.865
I'll deal with you later.

00:52:14.865 --> 00:52:17.025
Your head is really hard.

00:52:40.808 --> 00:52:44.302
- You can't do this without me, huh? - No, it's going fine!

00:52:45.938 --> 00:52:49.432
How did I trust you guys and run some guerrilla operation?

00:53:23.392 --> 00:53:26.562
Let's wrap this up already.

00:53:26.562 --> 00:53:29.138
I'm getting tired of it.

00:53:44.538 --> 00:53:47.165
Mr. Geum... Yoo In Goo...

00:53:47.165 --> 00:53:49.877
Ah, all my enemies are right here.

00:53:49.877 --> 00:53:52.296
Jeez, these scumbags!

00:53:52.296 --> 00:53:55.340
Mr. Han and Big boss,

00:53:55.340 --> 00:53:57.834
That sly Chairman Do,

00:53:59.428 --> 00:54:02.472
Even the martial arts master and Kang Beom Ryong.

00:54:02.472 --> 00:54:04.850
Just perfect, no need to track you all down one by one.

00:54:04.850 --> 00:54:07.060
That leech Yoo In Goo...

00:54:07.060 --> 00:54:10.522
What? Why did you bring them scrawny kids?

00:54:10.522 --> 00:54:13.474
If they join in too, this might get tricky for us.

00:54:14.943 --> 00:54:18.655
In Goo, who should we hit first?

00:54:18.655 --> 00:54:20.449
Who first...

00:54:20.449 --> 00:54:21.867
Can't we just take them all out at once?

00:54:21.867 --> 00:54:24.286
With just two hands, how can we hit everyone at once?

00:54:24.286 --> 00:54:25.746
You've got to set the order.

00:54:25.746 --> 00:54:27.530
Well...

00:54:30.584 --> 00:54:32.753
Yoo In Goo! What are you hesitating for?

00:54:32.753 --> 00:54:34.671
The ones who exposed your drug operation are those guys.

00:54:34.671 --> 00:54:36.632
- You should hit them. - That one...

00:54:36.632 --> 00:54:38.675
That one, start with that punk, that one!

00:54:38.675 --> 00:54:41.219
Me? Are you crazy?

00:54:41.219 --> 00:54:44.306
Those guys exposed the drugs, not me!

00:54:44.306 --> 00:54:47.726
Don't be ridiculous. I hate hearing that fake foreigner speak English the most.

00:54:47.726 --> 00:54:49.269
- Start with him. - Huh?

00:54:49.269 --> 00:54:50.771
In Won, that guy, that one.

00:54:50.771 --> 00:54:52.689
Hurry, hurry!

00:54:52.689 --> 00:54:54.390
Let's get out of here.

00:54:57.903 --> 00:55:00.113
What do we do? Huh?

00:55:00.113 --> 00:55:02.324
Take Gong Bok and get out.

00:55:02.324 --> 00:55:04.609
- Let's go, let's go! - Where?

00:55:36.942 --> 00:55:38.643
You little...

00:55:47.202 --> 00:55:48.903
What's this?

00:55:55.752 --> 00:55:58.130
What are you doing? Hurry up and finish it.

00:55:58.130 --> 00:55:59.831
Let's go.

00:56:00.716 --> 00:56:02.417
Slow down!

00:56:04.011 --> 00:56:05.721
- Hurry up, hurry! - Yes, yes, yes.

00:56:05.721 --> 00:56:06.888
Are you okay?

00:56:06.888 --> 00:56:08.589
Are you alright?

00:56:29.161 --> 00:56:30.287
Yoo In Goo!

00:56:30.287 --> 00:56:31.747
Yes, yes, yes.

00:56:31.747 --> 00:56:33.540
If you don't want to die, get out.

00:56:33.540 --> 00:56:35.241
Yes.

00:56:40.797 --> 00:56:42.549
Jeong Ho Myung.

00:56:42.549 --> 00:56:44.968
Hand over the item.

00:56:44.968 --> 00:56:47.429
If you draw a gun,

00:56:47.429 --> 00:56:49.797
Things will get serious.

00:56:50.515 --> 00:56:52.768
Once we get out of here,

00:56:52.768 --> 00:56:54.969
Cleaning this up will be easy.

00:57:00.442 --> 00:57:02.643
I'll say it one last time.

00:57:03.361 --> 00:57:05.354
Hand over the item!

00:57:33.642 --> 00:57:36.103
Alright, let's go.

00:57:36.103 --> 00:57:40.932
Still, we should at least pay for the item.

00:58:53.054 --> 00:58:54.755
Huh?

00:58:56.308 --> 00:58:57.350
It hurts...

00:58:57.350 --> 00:58:58.935
- What? - Are you conscious?

00:58:58.935 --> 00:59:00.687
Mr. Jeong!

00:59:00.687 --> 00:59:02.397
Ah... it... hurts...

00:59:02.397 --> 00:59:04.473
- I'll call an ambulance. - Yes.

00:59:05.192 --> 00:59:07.110
Hey, stay with me. Are you okay?

00:59:07.110 --> 00:59:09.353
It hurts, it hurts.

00:59:11.531 --> 00:59:12.824
Hey, wait. This really hurts.

00:59:12.824 --> 00:59:15.368
Of course, it hurts. You got shot.

00:59:15.368 --> 00:59:16.912
No, my hand...

00:59:16.912 --> 00:59:18.946
My hand hurts.

00:59:22.167 --> 00:59:23.668
Jeong Ho Myung!

00:59:23.668 --> 00:59:25.369
Are you okay?

00:59:26.671 --> 00:59:28.256
Help... help me...

00:59:28.256 --> 00:59:29.424
Just help me up.

00:59:29.424 --> 00:59:31.468
Man, you got shot. Why are you trying to get up?

00:59:31.468 --> 00:59:33.053
- Come on, hurry up. - I think he's okay.

00:59:33.053 --> 00:59:35.504
- Let's try to lift him. - Hurry, lift me up.

00:59:38.350 --> 00:59:40.968
- It hurts, it hurts! - One, two, three!

00:59:43.104 --> 00:59:44.648
It hurts!

00:59:44.648 --> 00:59:46.733
It hurts.

00:59:46.733 --> 00:59:48.068
Oh man, jeez...

00:59:48.068 --> 00:59:49.319
Oh, he's heavy.

00:59:49.319 --> 00:59:50.737
- Darn it. - Ouch, it hurts.

00:59:50.737 --> 00:59:52.322
It hurts, it hurts!

00:59:52.322 --> 00:59:54.449
Haven't got shot in ages. This really hurts.

00:59:54.449 --> 00:59:56.034
- You're so clumsy. - I'm dying here.

00:59:56.034 --> 00:59:57.077
You go around getting stabbed.

00:59:57.077 --> 00:59:58.703
Not stabbed, I got shot.

00:59:58.703 --> 00:59:59.913
- Oh right, you got shot. - What are you talking about?

00:59:59.913 --> 01:00:01.790
I'm feeling out of it.

01:00:01.790 --> 01:00:03.708
You two really lost your edge.

01:00:03.708 --> 01:00:04.709
Huh?

01:00:04.709 --> 01:00:05.919
What are you even talking about?

01:00:05.919 --> 01:00:08.630
I'm the one who helped you when you were all weak and barely standing.

01:00:08.630 --> 01:00:10.340
- I took care of everything today, all of it. - Jeez, you guys.

01:00:10.340 --> 01:00:12.926
If it weren't for me, both of you would be dead!

01:00:12.926 --> 01:00:14.803
I took down 42 people today.

01:00:14.803 --> 01:00:16.680
Did you hit the back of my head on purpose earlier?

01:00:16.680 --> 01:00:18.473
I didn't do it on purpose.

01:00:18.473 --> 01:00:20.758
Your head is really hard.

01:00:22.686 --> 01:00:24.479
Gently! It hurts!

01:00:24.479 --> 01:00:25.480
It hurts!

01:00:25.480 --> 01:00:27.223
Then shall I let go?

01:00:43.331 --> 01:00:45.166
Huh?

01:00:45.166 --> 01:00:46.876
What's this?

01:00:46.876 --> 01:00:47.877
Earth Defense Squad!

01:00:47.877 --> 01:00:50.204
Masked Racer!

01:01:01.808 --> 01:01:02.892
Jeong Ho Myung!

01:01:02.892 --> 01:01:05.261
You darn punk!

01:01:10.358 --> 01:01:13.528
<i>According to the latest interim prosecution report</i>

01:01:13.528 --> 01:01:17.115
<i>on the security crime case involving Candidate Han Kyung Wook,</i>

01:01:17.115 --> 01:01:20.285
<i>which shook the political world during the last mayoral election...</i>

01:01:20.285 --> 01:01:25.206
<i>Candidate Han is confirmed to have worked with North Korean Lieutenant Lee Cheol Jin</i>

01:01:25.206 --> 01:01:27.917
<i>and was involved in drug distribution 10 years ago.</i>

01:01:27.917 --> 01:01:31.546
<i>Repeated evidence shows he attempted to hand Yeongseondo Island over</i>

01:01:31.546 --> 01:01:33.840
<i>to an overseas criminal organization.</i>

01:01:33.840 --> 01:01:37.469
<i>Candidate Han Kyung Wook is also reported to be on trial today for multiple murders</i>

01:01:37.469 --> 01:01:39.387
<i>and conspiracy to commit murder.</i>

01:01:39.387 --> 01:01:43.266
<i>Authorities are intensively tracking Candidate Han's past activities</i>

01:01:43.266 --> 01:01:45.101
<i>while expanding the probe</i>

01:01:45.101 --> 01:01:47.395
<i>into the entire Yeongseondo Island development project</i>

01:01:47.395 --> 01:01:49.689
<i>he had pledged as a campaign promise.</i>

01:01:49.689 --> 01:01:52.108
<i>In particular, with evidence continuously emerging of links</i>

01:01:52.108 --> 01:01:55.820
<i>not only to domestic organizations but also to international crime networks,</i>

01:01:55.820 --> 01:01:57.697
<i>the investigation is reported</i>

01:01:57.697 --> 01:01:59.991
<i>to be unfolding as a large-scale joint operation</i>

01:01:59.991 --> 01:02:02.452
<i>beyond a single case.</i>

01:02:02.452 --> 01:02:04.579
<i>As a result, it is expected to take considerable time</i>

01:02:04.579 --> 01:02:06.790
<i>to fully uncover the truth,</i>

01:02:06.790 --> 01:02:08.666
<i>and further criminal details</i>

01:02:08.666 --> 01:02:12.379
<i>are likely to emerge step by step.</i>

01:02:12.379 --> 01:02:15.507
<i>Next up. At the Ja Ae-won Orphanage,</i>

01:02:15.507 --> 01:02:18.551
<i>the news that an anonymous donor</i>

01:02:18.551 --> 01:02:20.387
<i>left an expensive diamond</i>

01:02:20.387 --> 01:02:23.306
<i>has brought a subtle yet profound impact within the community.</i>

01:02:23.306 --> 01:02:26.476
<i>The diamond was recently discovered inside a small box</i>

01:02:26.476 --> 01:02:28.770
<i>left in front of the Ja Ae-won Orphanage's office,</i>

01:02:28.770 --> 01:02:30.855
<i>and the short handwritten note inside</i>

01:02:30.855 --> 01:02:35.810
<i>simply asked that it be used for the children.</i>

01:02:41.616 --> 01:02:43.943
[Ministry of Justice] I'm sorry!

01:02:49.457 --> 01:02:50.959
What? Me too, me too, me too!

01:02:50.959 --> 01:02:52.043
Take a picture together, together!

01:02:52.043 --> 01:02:54.620
Let's take a picture together.

01:02:59.342 --> 01:03:00.802
- Come quickly. - Uncle!

01:03:00.802 --> 01:03:03.587
- Mr. Bong, come quickly! - Hurry.

01:03:03.587 --> 01:03:07.592
[Jeongseok Study Residence]

01:03:10.145 --> 01:03:12.805
- Yes, yes, yes. - Let's take a picture.

01:03:18.111 --> 01:03:19.571
Well, Mr. Kim should be here by now.

01:03:19.571 --> 01:03:21.416
- What are you doing without me? - Come quickly, hurry!

01:03:21.416 --> 01:03:25.832
[O Ran Chinese Restaurant]

01:03:26.664 --> 01:03:30.431
[O Ran Chinese Restaurant]

